Kent, Washington Building Code Complaints (2017)

Kent, Washington (US)

This repository contains an analysis of building code complaints from the Code Enforcement office of the City of Kent, Washington.

It was created to supplement the Rental Housing Inspection Ordinance which was adpoted by the Kent City Council on March 20, 2018.
